00:19:40.167 --> 00:19:42.125
How are you doing this, Jane?

00:19:43.042 --> 00:19:48.393
JG: Well, I suppose, you know,
I'm obstinate, I don't like giving up,

00:19:48.417 --> 00:19:53.684
but I'm not going to let
