00:21:09.833 --> 00:21:12.309
wanting to tell Dr. Jane
what they've been doing

00:21:12.333 --> 00:21:14.101
to make the world a better place.

00:21:14.125 --> 00:21:15.934
How can I let them down?

00:21:15.958 --> 00:21:19.226
CA: I mean, as you look
at the planet's future,

00:21:19.250 --> 00:21:20.893
what worries you most, actually,

00:21:20.917 --> 00:21:24.292
