00:24:10.208 --> 00:24:14.351
JG: You know, just remember
that every day you live,

00:24:14.375 --> 00:24:16.726
you make an impact on the planet.

00:24:16.750 --> 00:24:19.018
You can't help making an impact.

00:24:19.042 --> 00:24:22.601
And at least, unless
you're living in extreme poverty,

00:24:22.625 --> 00:24:25.851
