00:24:53.500 --> 00:24:56.059
so they do nothing
and they become apathetic.

00:24:56.083 --> 00:24:58.875
And that is a huge danger, apathy.

00:24:59.750 --> 00:25:01.934
CA: Dr. Jane Goodall, wow.

00:25:01.958 --> 00:25:05.934
